The Atiku Presidential Campaign Organization on Monday appointed Segun Showunmi, a public affairs analyst, the official Spokesperson of the organization.

The organization in a statement on Monday, indicated that Showunmi, who was Special Assistant and Deputy Chief Press Secretary to the former Governor of Ogun State, Otunba Gbenga Daniel, had served in various political capacities, including the Jonathan/Sambo Campaign in 2011.



Former Vice President, Atiku Abubakar is a leading presidential aspirant of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP), and has been the rallying point of the party in the commitment to strengthen the Opposition Party and consolidate it for the 2019 general elections.

